This repository provides a reference implementation of the methods described in:

Veiga Rodrigues & Odderskov (2025).
"Climate error metrics based on Wasserstein distances".
Applied Energy, Volume 398, 126392.
DOI: 10.1016/j.apenergy.2025.126392
URL: https://doi.org/10.1016/j.apenergy.2025.126392
(Article metadata retrieved via the DOI registry / Crossref: https://api.crossref.org/works/10.1016/j.apenergy.2025.126392)


